OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775555970
OL,3,CLiverpool fans to stage protests
OL,4,Cagainst ticket price rises
OL,6,FLiverpool FC is facing a wave of
OL,7,Fsupporter backlash as fans prepare to
OL,8,Fstage a series of protests against
OL,9,Fupcoming ticket price increases.
OL,11,FThe move follows an announcement in
OL,12,FMarch 2026 that general admission
OL,13,Fprices will rise in line with
OL,14,Finflation for the next three seasons -
OL,15,Fdespite discussions with the
OL,16,FSupporters' Board who previously
OL,17,Fpetitioned for a freeze.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
