PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775555970
OL,3,CLiverpool fans to stage protests
OL,4,Cagainst ticket price rises
OL,6,FThe club ` which last season made a
OL,7,Fprofit after tax of #8million ` cited
OL,8,Fmatch day operating costs for the
OL,9,Fincrease, which have risen 85% since
OL,10,F2016-2017.
OL,12,FThe decision has been met with
OL,13,F"overwhelming opposition", with
OL,14,Fsupporters group Spirit of Shankly
OL,15,F(SoS) hastily arranging protests which
OL,16,Fwill begin at Saturday's home match
OL,17,Fwith Fulham.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
