FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775555970
OL,3,CLiverpool fans to stage protests
OL,4,Cagainst ticket price rises
OL,6,FA similar tactic in 2016, which saw
OL,7,Ffans stage a 70th-minute walkout
OL,8,Fagainst proposals for a #70 match
OL,9,Fticket, resulted in owners Fenway
OL,10,FSports Group performing a U-turn.
OL,12,F"Liverpool FC has chosen to ignore
OL,13,Fclear, overwhelming opposition from
OL,14,Fits own supporters and push ahead with
OL,15,Fplans to increase ticket prices for
OL,16,Fthe next three seasons," an SoS
OL,17,Fstatement said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775555970
OL,3,CLiverpool fans to stage protests
OL,4,Cagainst ticket price rises
OL,6,F"The open meeting online, the survey
OL,7,Fand countless conversations all point
OL,8,Fto the same thing: fans do not accept
OL,9,Fthis decision. If the club's owners
OL,10,Fwon't listen, then we make them.
OL,12,F"This is no longer about consultation.
OL,13,FThat opportunity has been and gone.
OL,14,FThis is about action. Protests inside
OL,15,Fand outside Anfield have been
OL,16,Fdiscussed. It is agreed they need to
OL,17,Fhappen.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775555970
OL,3,CLiverpool fans to stage protests
OL,4,Cagainst ticket price rises
OL,6,F"This will not be limited to one game.
OL,7,FAction will take place across home and
OL,8,Faway fixtures, starting with Fulham at
OL,9,FAnfield and escalating from there. The
OL,10,Fkey point is simple: this will grow
OL,11,Fand escalate."
OL,13,FSoS said the locking-in of prices for
OL,14,Fthree years removes "meaningful annual
OL,15,Fsecurity from supporters" and would
OL,16,Fset a precedent which could become
OL,17,Fprevalent across the Premier League if
OL,18,Fnot challenged.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@NO]vD@UOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775555970
OL,3,CLiverpool fans to stage protests
OL,4,Cagainst ticket price rises
OL,6,F"This decision sits with ownership.
OL,7,FThey have made the call. They can
OL,8,Freverse it," added the statement. "We
OL,9,Fwill be taking steps to make sure that
OL,10,Fmessage reaches them directly."
OL,12,FAmong the steps being implemented is a
OL,13,Fcall for fans not to spend money
OL,14,Finside the ground and to delay season
OL,15,Fticket renewals until close to the
OL,16,Fdeadline.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]pD@cOUrD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
