PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775555970
OL,3,CLiverpool fans to stage protests
OL,4,Cagainst ticket price rises
OL,6,FIt is understood Liverpool remain
OL,7,Fcommitted to meaningful consultation
OL,8,Fwith the Supporters' Board and while
OL,9,Fthey respect a right to protest, they
OL,10,Fare disappointed it is being viewed as
OL,11,Fthe next step.
OL,13,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,14,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,15,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,16,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
